\v 3 Awu ra atsurha ha abi irhΟΘrhΟΘ nu abi ibvuta, nu akatarhu nu abi ishayi iyor arh…¦rh…¦ aka isaka anu um…î.\f + \fr 5.3 \ft Abvur ak…î…î aki its…¦ng abok aki isha ag…îrke ik…¦i ug…¦, \fqa Ubinkutsu iva-ivanga ipfu itser-Num iki isaki icipuwa ru ukau am…¦ΧÉ hΟΘ iba idzipa ukp…î. Kishoo uwuruwi aka agbaashia atsΡ©ΟΘ ra am…¦ΧÉ hΟΘ ivangy…¦ ake aka idzipa amaa, unga awuri ikikerhunga irhΟΘrhΡ© iyornga kishoo.\f*
