\v 12 Angw…¦ΧÉ imesanga hΟΘ ag…¦, <<A Uteijee, aba awu urh…î, unga awuri ikerhunga.>>
\v 13 Ubin Uyesu aka arherhe ag…¦ Urhiazaru aka akpea, b…îr angw…¦ΧÉ imesanga akaif…¦rhk…î ag…¦ unga arherha arherhe urh…î uwuku uwosha.
