\v 17 Ivangy…¦ Uyesu aka azΡ© atsΡ©, ag≈© ug…¦ Urhiazaru aka akpea, umb…î aka adzake unga, aka amaa inuma inaa ru udzak.
\v 18 Ubetani ukhapa nggu Urusharhima, asi itsΡ©a akirhomita ataar.
\v 19 Abi Uyahuda arh…¦rh…¦ aba ighwe akpe Urhiazaru ru anapumb…î na ad…înge am…¦n Umarta nu Umaryamu.
\p 
\v 20 Ivangy…¦ Umarta aka ag≈© ug…¦ Uyesu uw…î abar…î, unga asok azΡ© agbanga unga. B…îr Umaryamu asei ri iya.
\p 
\v 21 Umarta ag…îr Uyesu ag…¦, <<A Uteijee, ag…¦ ungo uwu nggimi ungw…¦ΧÉm…¦n asi Ο≠kpea.
\v 22 B…îr uko ic…¦r…¦ umum ihw…¦ng Unum awuri idzaanga kishoo ubinkpi ungo iki ish…îΧÉrhΟΘ unga.>>
\p 
\v 23 Uyesu ag…îr unga ag…¦, <<Ungw…¦ΧÉmbi awuri isoka ik…¦i.>>
\p 
\v 24 Umarta ag…¦, <<Umum ihw…¦ng awuri ib…¦ka ik…¦i ri isisok abika akpukpe ri imimashu upfung.>>
